sections.heading: 16|Blackbird population control programs
sections.text: Effective:March 18, 1969Latest Legislation:House Bill 1 - 108th General AssemblyPDF:Download Authenticated PDF(A) As used in this section "blackbird" means the red-winged blackbird (Agelaius phoeniceus), the common grackle (Quiscalus quiscula), the brown-head
